# CLAUDE.md — redirect

All AI instructions for this project live in **AGENTS.md** (read by both Claude Code and Codex CLI). This redirect exists so Claude Code picks up the shared rules without duplicating them.

On session start, and after every context compaction, read AGENTS.md. When in doubt, run `/continue` to rebuild full context from AGENTS.md + SPEC.md + IMPLEMENTATION_NOTES.md.
